- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques such as attention-based neural networks for TTS.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses how to scale inference to handle large amounts of queries, which is related to system and control.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses deep learning techniques for TTS, which falls under machine learning.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper involves the use of AI techniques for TTS, such as attention-based neural networks and waveform synthesis methods.
